                                    "content": "We train AUTO- J from LLaMA- 2- 13B- chat (Touvron et al., 2023b) with the DeepSpeed (Rasley et al., 2020) library, Zero Redundancy Optimizer (ZeRO) (Rajbhandari et al., 2020) Ren et al., 2021) Stage 3, gradient checkpointing (Chen et al., 2016) and FlashAttention (Dao et al., 2022) Dao, 2023) on 8 NVIDIA A100 GPUs. We use the bfloat16 (BF16) and tfloat32 (TF32) mix computation precision"
